text: Young Doctors in Love is a 1982 American comedy movie directed by first time director Garry Marshall. It stars Michael McKean, Sean Young, Saul Rubinek, Harry Dean Staton, Hector Elizondo, Pamela Reed, Michael Richards, Dabney Coleman, Taylor Negron and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1982 comedy movies Category:1980s sex comedy movies Category:1980s teen comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Garry Marshall
